@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "FAQ";
}

<style>
    body {
        font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
    }

    h1, h2, h3 {
        color: #444;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-top: 30px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #ddd;
        padding-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .faq-question {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        cursor: pointer;
        position: relative;
    }

        .faq-question::after {
            content: '+';
            position: absolute;
            right: 0;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .faq-question.active::after {
            content: '-';
        }

    .faq-answer {
        display: none;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .faq-section {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
    }

        .faq-section p {
            text-align: justify;
        }
</style>

<h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

<div class="faq-section">
    <h2>General Questions</h2>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">What is HANDY RENT?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>HANDY RENT is a platform that allows users to rent various products and services directly from other users or businesses. Our goal is to make renting and leasing products easy and secure.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">How do I create an account?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>To create an account, click on "Register" at the top of the page, fill in your details, and follow the instructions. You will receive an email to confirm your registration.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Account and Login</h2>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">I forgot my password. What should I do?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>If you forgot your password, click on "Forgot password" on the login page. Enter your email address, and we will send you instructions to reset your password.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">How do I change my account details?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>To change your account details, log in and go to your profile page. There you can update your personal information and save the changes.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Renting</h2>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">How do I rent a product?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>To rent a product, search for the desired product on the website, select the rental period, and follow the payment instructions. Once your request is confirmed, you can arrange pickup or delivery with the renter.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Payments and Refunds</h2>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">What payment methods are accepted?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>We accept various payment methods, including credit cards, debit cards, and PayPal. All payments are securely processed through our payment gateway.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">How do refunds work?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>If you need a refund, contact customer service with your order ID and the reason for the refund. We process refunds according to our refund policy, which can take up to 7 business days to complete.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Contact and Support</h2>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">How can I contact customer service?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>You can contact our customer service by sending an email to support@HANDY RENT.com or calling our hotline at +45 1234 5678. We are available Monday to Friday from 9:00 AM to 5:00 PM.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">Where can I find more information?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>For more information, visit our help center, where you can find guides, tutorials, and additional resources.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
        const faqQuestions = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-question');

        faqQuestions.forEach(question => {
            question.addEventListener('click', function () {
                this.classList.toggle('active');
                const answer = this.nextElementSibling;
                if (answer.style.display === 'block') {
                    answer.style.display = 'none';
                } else {
                    answer.style.display = 'block';
                }
            });
        });
    });
</script>
